I"ˆ<h3 id="what-i-write">What I write</h3>

<p>My best writings are in theoretical biology. I take concepts that are easily mixed up and I separate them.</p>

<ul>
  <li>My <a href="https://ekernf01.github.io/tracerseq_short/">Tracer-seq discussion</a> separates clonal trees from lineage trees.</li>
  <li>My <a href="https://ekernf01.github.io/genetic_interactions/">critique of Perturb-ATAC</a> separates genetic interactions from statistical interactions.</li>
</ul>

